<p>For all the graded assignments (reading and problem sets), if you disagree
with the grading, you can discuss with me within two weeks after I return the <span
class=SpellE>homeworks</span>. After that, all the grades will be finalized. <a
name=prereq></a></p>

<h2>Prerequisites</h2>

<p>Students should have the background of basic database knowledge, and have
taken ICS184 and ICS214. In addition, students should know how to program in
languages such as C, C++, or Java. <a name=time></a></p>

<h2>Time and Place (Tentative)</h2>

<p>The class meets on Wednesday, 9.15 to 11.45 am, Location: 4348 Calit2
building ET</p>

